OAQueryTokenType
public class OAQueryTokenizer
extends java.lang.Object
implements OAQueryTokenType

Descendent parser internally used to parse object queries into a Vector of OAQueryToken Objects. Uses a OAQueryTokenManager to parse into tokens.

For more information about this package, see documentation.
